!   Arithmetic

    variable X
    variable Y
    variable Z
    variable Sum
    
    put 5 into X
    put 7 into Y
    add X to Y
    alert `5 added to 7 makes ` cat Y
    
    multiply Y by 3 giving Z
    alert `12 multiplied by 3 makes ` cat Z
    
    take X from Z giving Sum
    alert `36 take away 5 makes ` cat Sum
